title: Ice Cube Interview and more

description:
Today on the show we had Ice Cube call in where he spoke about the contract with black America, Reconstructing the system and more. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a 29 year old woman who shot her boyfriend for not wanting to argue and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
